    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/9d3e457f59d84829d197c0f463207687.poster.avif?t=1748953798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/9d3e457f59d84829d197c0f463207687.webm?t=1748953798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/9d3e457f59d84829d197c0f463207687.mp4?t=1748953798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扮演超级英雄</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个激动人心的砍杀和第三人称射击混合游戏中，你将扮演屠杀队长——一个强悍的超级英雄，保护世界免受各种超级恶棍的侵害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/6b50dee874154a43501271505b93d53f.poster.avif?t=1748953798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/6b50dee874154a43501271505b93d53f.webm?t=1748953798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/6b50dee874154a43501271505b93d53f.mp4?t=1748953798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >对抗强大的超级恶棍</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将您的个人技能与英雄的超能力和武器相结合，在不同地点击败强大的恶棍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/faa6402ce6f746e8c5c301e8c5855f96.poster.avif?t=1748953798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/faa6402ce6f746e8c5c301e8c5855f96.webm?t=1748953798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/faa6402ce6f746e8c5c301e8c5855f96.mp4?t=1748953798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >黑色讽刺幽默</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在成为超级英雄之前，屠杀队长只是一个运气异常糟糕的普通人。有一天，他发现自己正卷入一场争夺高科技血清的超人之战。通过一系列不幸的事件，他被注射了血清并获得了超能力——增强的战斗力、加快的速度和再生能力。屠杀队长凭借新获得的能力，以全职员工的身份加入了一个可疑的超级英雄组织。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/97c971f2a5b74ecb7a74b050b15c196d.poster.avif?t=1748953798\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/97c971f2a5b74ecb7a74b050b15c196d.webm?t=1748953798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240950/extras/97c971f2a5b74ecb7a74b050b15c196d.mp4?t=1748953798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随心所欲地改变你的游戏风格</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用所有近战和远程攻击来击败你的对手！</p>",
